** Basic installation **

make
make install

** Non-root installation **

Put the executable "pager" at ~/.sawfish/, and the lisp files pager.jl(c)
at ~/.sawfish/lisp/sawfish/wm/ext/.

** Upgrading notes **

When you upgrade from an older version, make sure you reload both the
lisp module and the executable, for example by restarting
sawfish. Versions are not intercompatible with older ones!

** Notes **

Sawfish version older than 1.6.1 are not supported with this version.
If you need support for them, refer back to v0.7.2.
